DATE:
From Friday, November 1st to Monday, November 4th
※The opening hours are as follows
Nov. 1st: 13:00 - 20:00
Nov. 2nd and 3rd: 10:00 - 20:00
Nov. 4th: 10:00 - 17:00
※Admission Free

GALLERY:

Sandanzaka no Wakan
